{"type": "article", "id": 3388, "title": "阿斯顿马丁& Silver Cross 限量版婴儿车", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-10T07:44:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052327318eoZbhW4AsJNLYfD.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国豪华跑车制造商阿斯顿·马丁日前联手英国著名折叠婴儿车制造商 Silver Cross 推出了一款限量版的联名折叠婴儿车「Surf Aston Martin Edition 2014」，超轻的镁合金结构与阿斯顿马丁的铝合金车轮为这款婴儿车提供空气悬挂避震功能，手工缝制的皮质手柄与超轻的防水材质顶棚，也为这部婴儿车提供了更为舒适的内部环境。此外，它的座椅可提供 3 种倾斜角度，并且可以实现完全平躺。「Surf Aston Martin Edition 2014」全球限量 800 辆，每一辆都刻有限量版徽章的编码，定价 3000 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.harrods.com/product/surf-aston-martin-edition-2014/silver-cross/000000000004610564\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232730dPz6Wny5aV0k7cEo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232730u0wsDm2UyYcZ58NC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232730UPBpG89bYWRKwXmc.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523273197yKaidXs6cZjNJL.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}